	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I disagree with those stating that this spell is useless.  Being a low level wizard, I find it hard to get into groups at times, so I end up going solo.  I use this spell whenever I overpull during my soloing.  It's got a quick casting time, and I love dropping three gnolls at once (yes, I've done this numerous times).  As a little background information, at 9th level, I still go into melee quite often... mostly to practice my melee skills (2hb, 1hb, and piercing are all maxed), but also because root is unpredictable - lasts the entire fight one time, and breaks instantly the next.<BR>
<BR>
If anyone wants me to prove my mettle with this spell, contact Orendar on Erolissi Marr sometime.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
